000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/111016_320fa7e6b876762e5b1d45ebf4799677.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F111016_320fa7e6b876762e5b1d45ebf4799677.png&h=a62f9028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主係隱性五毛個個都知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:16:15.000Z","msg":"個個都知就唔係隱性啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143308fda1e7133b42647426c444f75a9f14b6c3","tid":798720,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:38:27.000Z","msg":"十卜ching 同毛潤之兩隻五毛狗又一齊開工"},{"pid":"9792477b0278ef5119651e5138e7c9df858db6ac","tid":798720,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:39:42.000Z","msg":"廢撚到，被人拉膽量都冇，仲柒過泛民<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/303747\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/303747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來五毛狗毛澤東扮晒正義話我指羅冠聰抵打係五毛狗 佢隻五毛狗呢頭就屌陳浩天無膽量俾人拉，五毛狗果然係講一套做一套，最重要有位入你[/quote]<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/07/29/h48SI2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2Fh48SI2.png&h=8276f73a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五毛狗毛澤東真係賤種仆街黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請注意,五毛狗毛潤之#90863竟然恥笑陳浩天無膽量俾人拉，個post 仲要得佢一班五毛同事幫推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/760904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/760904</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e3b0f3ec57ab8a26dd9699dc8597c2b8db61207f","tid":798720,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:41:56.000Z","msg":"五毛狗毛澤東對1000歲有利用價值個陣就引用，針對佢個陣就投訴 以下可以睇下五毛狗毛澤東係幾咁人渣，陰毒<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/09/iyYwSs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2FiyYwSs.png&h=8bc6f964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/09/DBKyVw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2FDBKyVw.png&h=3ca146e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/09/1c7bmZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F1c7bmZ.png&h=fd8f8d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有佢成日同出名五毛狗三色貓 jr仲有十卜ching一齊開工 一早俾人放過入list,仲有其他巴打都知佢係五毛狗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/09/TzuJrb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2FTzuJrb.png&h=881d1508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/07/29/pNE2bH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2FpNE2bH.png&h=94a80a84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同五毛合作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/09/Ybxowu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2FYbxowu.png&h=9b2c169a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/09/HtsLGJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2FHtsLGJ.png&h=e40f9f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五毛狗毛澤東仲要恥笑埋陳浩天<br />\n請注意,五毛狗毛潤之#90863竟然恥笑陳浩天無膽量俾人拉，個post 仲要得佢一班五毛同事幫推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/760904\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/760904</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他五毛狗毛潤之仆街野請睇<br />\n大家注意，毛潤之#90863係五毛狗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/760013\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/760013</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n澄清下關於五毛狗毛澤東屈我係五毛呢件事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/422926\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/422926</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最新五毛list（丁酉年秋重編版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/406007\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/406007</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0b4853f6c1f1250393d326c099d285294cc24abb","tid":798720,"uid":1380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:36:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"